  "title": "Logistic Officer - 6 months (Convertible to Perm) // Labrador",
  "description": "<h1><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h1><ul><li>Coordinate with the factory to send invoices and follow up on all required supporting documents, such as manufacturing certificates. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTkyMjY2OTc4NiJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Manage and process order revisions due to breakages, ensuring all updates are finalized before issuing invoices based on factory notifications. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTI0MTkyNDE0In0%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Review and update the Carrier’s Bill of Lading (B/L) where necessary. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMzc2ODA0MzY0In0%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Check margin details and validate all information prior to invoice confirmation.<a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiOTM1MTUzNjk2In0%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Consolidate, verify, amend, and send the full set of export documents to the Order Team. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTk1ODE5MjQzNiJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Handle LC/DA/DP transactions — prepare documentation, gather signatures, and submit the necessary documents to the bank or customers. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTQ3ODc2MjUyMyJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Apply for marine insurance, review policy details, and obtain the marine insurance certificate.<a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMjA5NjE0NTA5OSJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Submit tax invoices to the Finance Department. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiOTE2NTk4OTU1In0%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Prepare and maintain weekly and monthly reports as required</li></ul><p><br />a {    text-decoration: none;    color: #464feb;}tr th, tr td {    border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;}tr th {    background-color: #f5f5f5;}</p><h1><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h1><ul><li>Minimum NITEC qualification in any field.<a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTIzMDYwNTg2NCJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>0–2 years of relevant working experience. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTk2MDUxODIyIn0%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Professional, pleasant, and mature demeanor with strong customer service orientation. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTczMzQxMDc3NSJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Ability to multitask and work independently with minimal supervision. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTE3ODE3ODQ5MyJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Preferably familiar with shipping and manufacturing processes. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTEzNTY0NjI5NCJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Advantageous to have knowledge of Incoterms and import/export documentation. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiMTc1MzQ5MzMxMCJ9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>Strong customer service skills. <a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiODQwMjUyMDkyIn0%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></li><li>General understanding of global events and issues that may impact shipping activities. </li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the above positions, please click \"Apply now\" </p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. </p><p>JAC Recruitment Pte. Ltd. </p><p>EA License No: 90C3026</p><p>EA Personnel No: R23113652</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Yi Lei<a href=\"https://jacsingapore-my.sharepoint.com/personal/yilei_wong_jac-recruitment_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B9A332446-1869-4324-B142-3619449525F2%7D&file=Supply%20Chain%20Management%20Officer%20-%206%20months%20contract.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true&nav=eyJoIjoiOTkzMTA0MzQifQ%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
